    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160920/extras/b3a259773a380fdb2e5d28d9eb895cd9.avif?t=1770658789\" width=1024 height=307 /></span><strong><u>These Bungos are not messing around</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pummel your friends with over the top attacks, huge combos and giant frying pans!???</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160920/extras/1111bbae19d9998ddc79b445817ee747.poster.avif?t=1770658789\" aria-label=\"Bungo Bash combo attack\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160920/extras/1111bbae19d9998ddc79b445817ee747.webm?t=1770658789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160920/extras/1111bbae19d9998ddc79b445817ee747.mp4?t=1770658789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160920/extras/bf2d247ce81f32ca8a7d41b8e104a8ea.avif?t=1770658789\" width=1024 height=596 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u> </u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160920/extras/ade83b00e59f83e5a14886d535b15f37.avif?t=1770658789\" width=1024 height=283 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Supa Fun Items!</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yep you can play with items on! Jetpack around the stage, shoot Bungos with coconuts and blow em up with blueberry bombs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><u>Lots to Master!</u></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to become a Bungo pro there is a lot to learn. DI, bouncestepping, parrys, neutral, combos etc… We plan to host online tournaments every week and also IRL one</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160920/extras/a5223f8dc1ff71d4e6b6786545725e86.poster.avif?t=1770658789\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160920/extras/a5223f8dc1ff71d4e6b6786545725e86.webm?t=1770658789\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160920/extras/a5223f8dc1ff71d4e6b6786545725e86.mp4?t=1770658789\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3160920/extras/072788015ff585c0e1421b06e4ae5780.avif?t=1770658789\" width=1024 height=428 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a Bungo! See behind the scenes updates, make your voice heard and battle it out on our weekly playtests!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
